comments: Created 1.4.1896 out of the parish of Mumby.

Abolished 24.3.1888 and added to the parish of Wainfleet 
    All Saints.

Abolished 1.4.1936 and added to the parish of Langton by 
    Spilsby.

Created 25.3.1882 out of the parishes of Frieston, Leverton, 
    Hareby, Hundleby, Mavis Enderby, Raithby and West Keal. See also Table 2, note 
    (d).

Abolished 1.4.1926 and divided between the parishes of Skegness 
    and Addlethorpe.
